messages.content:
Step-by-step reasoning:
- The user wants to turn on the LR1-FRONT FOYER_SW device to 75% brightness.
- This should happen at 6 PM every day.
- The action should only occur if the device is currently off (Status = 0%).
- The command to turn on with a specific level is On [DON] with parameter 75% or On Level [OL] with 75%.
- Since the device accepts On [DON] with a parameter for level, we can use that.
- The condition is COS check that Status is 0% (off).
- The time condition is time equals 18:00 (6 PM).
- The action is to send On [DON] with parameter 75%.

{
  "routine": {
    "name": "Turn on foyer light to 75% at 6 PM if off",
    "condition": {
      "and": [
        {
          "==": {
            "device": "LR1-FRONT FOYER_SW",
            "status": "Status",
            "value": 0,
            "uom": "percent",
            "precision": 1
          }
        },
        {
          "==": [
            {"var": "time.hour"},
            18
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    "action": {
      "device": "LR1-FRONT FOYER_SW",
      "command": "On",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "On Level",
          "value": 75,
          "uom": "percent",
          "precision": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
